This is a collection statement in relation to the activities in the dropdown menus below. Choose the box relevant to you for more information.  Read this in conjunction with the
ABC Privacy Policy
.
If you are a child have a look at the
ABC Privacy Collection Statement (for young people)
.
Sometimes it may be possible for you to provide information to the ABC without disclosing your real identity. For example, signing up for an ABC Account or an ABC iview Account using an email address that does not include your name and using a nickname.
Other times this will not be possible, for example where you must disclose your identity before being granted entry to the ABC studio as an audience member.
To understand who the ABC may
share your personal information with please read this section.
You don’t have to give us all the information we ask for, but this may limit how we interact with you, and the services that we can provide.
We collect, hold, use and disclose your personal information when you:
Register for an ABC Account
The data we collect may be used for the following purposes:
ABC Account administration;
helping us understand more about the composition, interests, and behaviours of our audiences to see whether we are reaching a broad cross-section of Australians in accordance with our objectives;
helping our audiences find content likely to be of interest to them including by giving recommendations. As  an ABC Account holder you still have access to all of our content and can choose content independently of our recommendations, or you can opt-out of recommendations via your Account Settings if you prefer;
performing research and analysis, including receiving anonymised, aggregated reports, aimed at improving our content, services and reach;
providing you with information about ABC activities, products, services and events that may be of interest to you - this includes promotions for ABC content on third party digital services as well as ABC digital services; and
combining your account information with data we collect about your use of our digital services, including behavioural and location data, and other information you provide to the ABC. This combined information may include data that we have already collected about you.
If you are a registered ABC Account holder, we may disclose a hashed version of your email address to Google and Meta, via a technology service provider called Tealium, to show you promotions for ABC content likely to be of interest to you on those platforms.  For an explanation of hashing technology and how it is used, including how to opt-out, please click
here
.
If you are not a registered ABC Account holder, or you are accessing an ABC digital platform while not logged into your ABC Account, we may disclose the identifier for your device or browser to Google and Meta, via Tealium, for the same purposes. This will only occur if you have opted-in to the use of device identifiers or cookies for marketing purposes.
If you sign up for an ABC Account via another account such as Google or Meta, we will receive your email address, first name, year of birth, gender, and location. We may also receive a link to your profile photo, but only if you give your consent to that platform.
For privacy controls that restrict personalised advertising based on your choices across digital networks more broadly, you can read
more information about that here
.
Register your interest to participate as an ABC audience member
When you register your interest to participate as an ABC audience member we will collect personal information from you. If we ask for sensitive information, we will also ask for your consent to use that sensitive information.  Sometimes, you may not be able to participate unless you provide us with sensitive information.
The data we collect may be used for the following purposes:
administer your registration as an ABC audience member;
help us understand more about the composition and diversity of our audiences;
perform research and analysis aimed at improving our content and services; and
provide you with information about ABC activities, products, services and events that may interest you.
Sign up to receive an ABC newsletter or enter a competition
When you sign up to receive an ABC newsletter or enter a competition or promotion, we will collect personal information from you including your preferences and interests.
The data we collect may be used for the following purposes:
administer your registration for an ABC newsletter, event, competition or campaign;
help us understand more about the composition, needs and behaviours of our audiences to see whether we are reaching a broad cross-section of Australians in accordance with our objectives;
help our audiences find content likely to be of interest to them including by giving recommendations. ABC Account holders still have access to all of our content and can choose content independently of our recommendations if they prefer;
perform research and analysis aimed at improving our content, services and reach; and
Participate in research or surveys and address your queries
When you participate in research, surveys or submit a query, we will collect personal information from you.  We will also collect the specific information about the research being conducted.
If we ask for sensitive information, we will also ask for your consent to use that sensitive information.  Sometimes, you may not be able to participate unless you provide us with sensitive information.
The data we collect may be used for the following purposes:
conduct surveys;
perform research and analysis aimed at improving our content and services;
address your queries;
help us understand more about the composition, needs and behaviours of our audiences, so we can reflect and represent the Australian community in our content and services; and
manage our relationship with you.
More information on the following topics is available in the
ABC Privacy Policy
.
Promotions through digital platforms
Combining your personal information
Disclosure and use of your personal information
Overseas disclosures of your personal information
